  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), camera=(), microphone=(), accelerometer=(), gyroscope=(), magnetometer=(), ambient-light-sensor=(), speaker-selection=(), display-capture=(), payment=(), publickey-credentials-get=(), identity-credentials-get=(), storage-access=(), browsing-topics=(), interest-cohort=(), web-share=(), clipboard-read=(), clipboard-write=(), autoplay=(self), fullscreen=(self), picture-in-picture=(self), encrypted-media=(self), screen-wake-lock=(), usb=(), serial=(), bluetooth=(), hid=(), idle-detection=(), local-fonts=(), window-management=(), keyboard-map=(), gamepad=(), xr-spatial-tracking=(), sync-xhr=(), unload=()
